/plans/

# UI build toolchain deps.
/internal/server/ui/node_modules/

# Built UI bundles (hashed JS/CSS/fonts) AND the index.html that references them
# are generated by `make ui` and are NOT committed — they're large and their
# hashed asset refs churn on every build (tracking index.html caused recurring
# merge conflicts on its bundle-hash line). `//go:embed all:static` still
# compiles because the brand SVGs stay tracked; run `make ui` (or `make build`,
# which auto-builds the UI when assets are missing) to produce a working UI.
# A clean clone must `make ui` once before the UI renders.
/internal/server/static/assets/
/internal/server/static/index.html
